releases.name: v0.7.0
releases.body:
## Release v0.7.0

docs(MkDocs): update `mkdocs.yml`

## Changelog
### Features
* ed7da9c585b5dd10539039d5f0683787f469065e: feat(checks): replace language-specific checks with releasekit integration (@grokify)
### Bug Fixes
* 14b6fb23209aab446a55a38a4c015797adfa7191: fix(checks): remove unused helper functions (@grokify)
### Refactoring
* 5761d0a01df7a1da37aabe43bcade9b4414c27b3: refactor(plugins): restructure plugin layout with specs directory (@grokify)
### Other
* ea734a4a5c961fa2373c19b22b5079eef5ee003a: build(deps): bump github.com/agentplexus/multi-agent-spec/sdk/go (@dependabot[bot])
* 747b7c4275d21ab210f0f69c896944943775b3ba: chore(checks): remove obsolete language-specific checkers (@grokify)
* 737f1d2536c969494516e8a3c7d70a33986e868a: docs(MkDocs): update `mkdocs.yml` (@grokify)
* 813cc53c455f063738d0779c1ea7a6ec6f4254a3: docs(agents): expand agent documentation with detailed workflows (@grokify)

---

**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/agentplexus/agent-team-release/compare/v0.6.0...v0.7.0

### Installation

```bash
# Go install
go install github.com/agentplexus/agent-team-release/cmd/atrelease@v0.7.0

# Homebrew (macOS/Linux)
brew tap agentplexus/tap
brew install atrelease
```

releases.name: v0.6.0
releases.body:
## Release v0.6.0

refactor!: rename binary from `releaseagent` to `atrelease`

## Changelog
### Features
* a07def7b1ec41bac131265d63ba59d9c295ed34d: feat(cli): add `install kiro` command with embedded agent files (@grokify)
* 6a1ef4d2503bd56f4c33c259eff58c15f6478770: feat(specs): add skill specifications for commit-classification and version-analysis (@grokify)
### Refactoring
* 51bb23fe0f9e1f8afaf6bd7b838d0bbe37050c30: refactor!: rename binary from `releaseagent` to `atrelease` (@grokify)
* 99926c972c1b05dbe29966805f650562fba808e3: refactor!: rename project from release-agent-team to agent-team-release (@grokify)
* 5a1443044771f9a0255df367515a120d713a0e72: refactor(plugins/kiro): restructure agents with tools/allowedTools arrays (@grokify)
* 5336159380b04ee1b72e3d187841f54fecab039d: refactor(specs): add allowedTools field and update Claude plugin (@grokify)
### Other
* 7bd6a87e18835e60ebcae7f926d8c59f3ed03c4f: chore(ci): `release.yaml`: update go versions (@grokify)
* 34aa944fd2f12c14b09291f3d1276f89db989c03: chore(deps): `go mod`: update (@grokify)

---

**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/agentplexus/agent-team-release/compare/v0.5.1...v0.6.0

### Installation

```bash
# Go install
go install github.com/agentplexus/agent-team-release/cmd/atrelease@v0.6.0

# Homebrew (macOS/Linux)
brew tap agentplexus/tap
brew install atrelease
```

releases.name: v0.5.0
releases.body:
## Release v0.5.0

docs: update changelog for v0.5.0

## Changelog
### Features
* d72d66813edd3fd4b50c5890df745ef0b15ab918: feat(report): add DAG dependency tracking for team ordering (@grokify)
* 9011cac8f49ec29a5a87e4d3ab04e3a2f2d77019: feat(workflow): make release-validation depend on all validation steps (@grokify)
* 5fc0e7262cc5be98fb7901e3f89fcc440d0294b2: feat: add PM validation and multi-agent IR for v0.5.0 (@grokify)
* 734385fc6497a8f54745327f01646eff064b745f: feat: add team spec loader and improve report header (@grokify)
### Bug Fixes
* 1c8adae927ad411cc7e62aa7a3879aad01c51d62: fix(docs): add missing PM  Release edge in DAG diagram (@grokify)
* 187b71f0c639b40675d4224a49bf7aea72cba44c: fix(docs): use darker text colors in DAG diagram for dark mode (@grokify)
* 19d086378fabae88078ad534164d2059efac8cfa: fix(security): exclude security.go from hardcoded secrets scan (@grokify)
### Refactoring
* cfa5497e69238e278c99b5d396c211b7819f505f: refactor(report): use multiagentspec types from multi-agent-spec SDK (@grokify)
* be6a15a44ce997f2303a2643070e9751ab6a4ad3: refactor: consolidate agent/team/deployment specs under specs/ directory (@grokify)
* 9f8b2c0ae769b9caa5f823fc281ff1d4756679cc: refactor: update to multi-agent-spec SDK v0.2.0 (@grokify)
* e3ff5ef52380dace94c1f33f494f9f6e6410587e: refactor: update to multi-agent-spec SDK v0.3.0 (@grokify)
### Other
* e0f5e7868ab89ed011ebf96ecce94c6c50bd71fb: docs(README.md): fix formatting (@grokify)
* d35d8be63ad02a7b00388fe2987e1b53df5bd05a: docs(multi): update to name as "Release Agent Team" (@grokify)
* 5c2e958b6157123a5e5474ec81e62a4abf551976: test(report): update tests to use multiagentspec types (@grokify)

---

**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/agentplexus/release-agent-team/compare/v0.4.0...v0.5.0

### Installation

```bash
# Go install
go install github.com/agentplexus/release-agent-team/cmd/releaseagent@v0.5.0

# Homebrew (macOS/Linux)
brew install agentplexus/tap/release-agent-team
```
